`/newsyntax
#include <vcc.h>

typedef int (*TF)(int x)
  _(requires x > 1)
  _(ensures \result > 0);

int bar(int x)
  _(requires x > 0)
  _(ensures \result > 1);

void foo() {
  TF p = &bar;
  int res = p(3);
  _(assert res > 0)
}
`
Verification of foo succeeded.
